Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:30.68,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}明天就會結上層痂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:36.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur6}從海角邊 開出葉舟
